Margaret Kerry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Kerry 0 Margaret Kerry (born May 11, 1929) is an American actress and radio host, best known for her 1953 work as the model for Tinker Bell in the Walt Disney Pictures animated feature, Peter Pan.
